# Media player controls
bindsym XF86AudioPlay exec amixer -D pulse set Master 1+ toggle
bindsym XF86AudioPause exec amixer -D pulse set Master 1+ toggle
bindsym XF86AudioNext exec playerctl next
bindsym XF86AudioPrev exec playerctl previous

